{"tid":1381349,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方改裝警棍 ??","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:01:58.000Z","uid":157816,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69f2752576f70882cfcffa12ce7a9eae85c0a283","tid":1381349,"uid":157816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:17:32.000Z","msg":"借post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1381208/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1381208/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><blockquote><br />\n部門：警務處警察公共關係科 <br />\n稿號：GIS2019072900581<br />\n警方澄清<br />\n＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n就有媒體報道，指有警務人員於七月二十七日在元朗西鐵站內執勤時使用改裝警棍，以增加殺傷力，警方今日（七月二十九日）作出以下澄清：<br />\n<br />\n該名警務人員使用的警棍尾部繫有膠索帶，用以固定警棍尾部的繩。由於他在使用警棍時繩子鬆脫，令膠索帶由警棍尾部滑到警棍前方，因而引起誤會。<br />\n<br />\n此外，亦有網上言論就該名警務人員的身份存疑，警方證實該名人員是現職警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月29日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間15時29分<br />\n</blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n咁屯門依碌又乜鳩野黎<br />\n棍頭棍尾都有唔同喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWTTQkt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWTTQkt.png&h=d1731480&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aead812d21f207d2d15f7f2d762df3958ed42873","tid":1381349,"uid":157816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"e580825f46f73ff67124e7478bc144db5d3d0be8","tid":1381349,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:21:40.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"97f5b50b08f2af9571f5407cc868a992a9b1624e","tid":1381349,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"ec7206241d59ad85cda2b3dc9041c40a6234a0e7","tid":1381349,"uid":157816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":